rows.label: qst200827_msg0001
rows.name:
You can't beat us anymore,
so just give up...

rows.label: qst200827_msg0002
rows.name:
And we don't have any
classified documents...

rows.label: qst200827_msg0004
rows.name:
I said I had a carefully
planned strategy, didn't I?

rows.label: qst200827_msg0005
rows.name: I know you cherish the Saffronia tree.

rows.label: qst200827_msg0006
rows.name:
I'll burn the Saffronia tree until
you hand over the documents.

rows.label: qst200827_msg0007
rows.name:
What?! How could you do
something so horrible!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0008
rows.name:
Those children have
nothing to do with this!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0010
rows.name: I've finally gained the upper hand...

rows.label: qst200827_msg0011
rows.name:
Can you see? Aren't three of
them burning? My comrades
diligently set them on fire.

rows.label: qst200827_msg0012
rows.name:
If you don't want any more
to burn, hand over the
classified documents.

rows.label: qst200827_msg0013
rows.name: I told you I don't have them!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0014
rows.name:
Everyone! It's useless talking to
him. Let's go put out the fire!

rows.label: qst200827_msg0016
rows.name:
I think it would be faster
to give me the documents
than to put out the fire...

rows.label: qst200827_msg0017
rows.name:
Well, if you change your mind, bring
them to me. Until then, I'll burn as
many Saffronia trees as I like!
